<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.8">
<l>aravunīḷ koṭiyō ṉavaiyuḷā caṉattai yañciṭā tēyiṭa vataṟkup</l>
<l>periyamā mēṉi yaṇṭamū ṭuruvap perunticai yaṭaṅkiṭa nimirntōṉ</l>
<l>varaiyiṉmā maṇiyum marakatat tiraḷum vayiramum vetirutir muttum</l>
<l>tiraikoṇarn tunti vayaltoṟuṅ kuvikkun tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who grew so that the vast quarters were completely encompassed</l>
<l rend="indent">so that his huge, great body pierced through the firmament,</l>
<l>For that [time] when the one whose high banner is a serpent</l>
<l rend="indent">placed without fear a [false] seat in the assembly,</l>
<l>Stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi where waves,</l>
<l rend="indent">carrying huge gems from the mountains, emerald orbs,</l>
<l>Diamonds, and pearls which drop from bamboo, casting [them] up,</l>
<l rend="indent">heap [them] in every field.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
